<P><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> thing could exceed the mi&s;erable &s;tate of the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters">rtly after the return of Verus. In this <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="4 letters">ture was repre&s;ented an emperor, unawed <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters">ple, or the calamities &s;urrounding him, giv|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> to unheard of debaucheries. A raging pe&s;ti|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="5 letters"> &s;preading terror and de&s;olation through all
